OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright start for most, with
OL,6,Fany morning low cloud quickly lifting
OL,7,Fand clearing away. Then a much sunnier
OL,8,Fday than of late for all, with
OL,9,Fgenerally light winds. Feeling warmer
OL,10,Fas a result.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FPlenty of sunshine through
OL,13,Fthe evening, then staying clear
OL,14,Fovernight. Some mist and fog patches
OL,15,Fforming during the early hours.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FMorning fog patches quickly
OL,18,Fclearing to leave a fine and very warm
OL,19,Fday, with plenty of sunshine. Perhaps
OL,20,Fa little cloud returning to parts of
OL,21,FCumbria at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
