OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FHigh
OL,6,Fpressure keeping it dry and settled.
OL,7,FPlenty of sunshine and feeling hot.
OL,8,FSome overnight low cloud and fog
OL,9,Fforming each night but quickly
OL,10,Fclearing during the early mornings.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
